Project: CORE HR Infrastructure (Banking Sector)

Worked on developing and maintaining a CORE HR Infrastructure application used in the banking sector to manage large-scale employee data and HR transactions. 
The system was built using ASP.NET MVC, .NET Core, C#, Entity Framework Core, Hangfire, and SQL Server. 
Responsibilities included developing and enhancing application features, building RESTful APIs, optimizing database queries, 
and automating background processes using Hangfire.

Additionally, handled production support and error monitoring by tracking application logs using Serilog, analyzing production issues,
identifying root causes, and fixing bugs to ensure high system availability, reliability, and smooth business operations.
